item.title: Contact
item.description: About these pages # The resources on these pages are predominantly intended for use by undergraduate, postgraduate, and PhD students wishing to learn to use the powerful (yet initially complex) EEGLAB and ERPLAB software for data preprocessing. The website is owned & maintained by Jen Lewendon, postdoctoral researcher at New York Universit Abu Dhabi. For any enquiries, help, or further information, contact Jen via her personal webpages here. Whilst a myriad of resources exist for the novice ERP researcher, the information on this website aims to fill a gap.
